}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== '''[[ASUS]]''''s firmware seems to indicate this device is [[Ralink]]/[[TrendChip]] based..
===Specifications=== :per ''ASUS'''s product page * ''Memory'': 16MB Flash, 64MB DDR2 * ''Antenna'': 2x Detachable 2dBi antenna * ''Ports'': 4x RJ45 10/100 BaseT for LAN, 1x RJ11 for xDSL *''USB Ports'': 1x USB 2.0 * ''Power Adapter'': AC Input: 100~240V (50~60HZ), DC Output: 12 V/1 A *''Dimensions (W x H x D)'': 123 mm x 35 mm x 190 mm *''Weight'': 314 g
